Killing

The Stalker can kill anyone, and every kill will immediately cause electricity sabotage (if electricity is already sabotaged, nothing will happen). Stalker cannot vent. If the wins while the Stalker is alive or the wins by killing the (according to the host's setting, the Stalker may also win when the wins by killing the Neutrals), then the Stalker win alone.

  • Kill Cooldown
    • Set how long a Stalker has to wait to kill.
  • Has Vision
    • : the Stalker has the same vision as an Impostor
    • : the Stalker has default vision
  • When win by killing a player, they can snatch the victory
    • : the Stalker can steal a Victory if the win by killing/voting a player
    • : the Stalker will not steal the victory
  • Snatches Victory
    • : the Stalker can steal the win from anyone as long as the Stalker is alive
    • : the Stalker will not steal the win from anyone

From: TOHY
